videos.description: 1H (15:10) UNC Justin Jackson made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Kennedy Meeks.
videos.headline: Great passing leads to Justin Jackson 3.
SYR vs. UNC

videos.description: North Carolina seniors Marcus Paige and Brice Johnson relive a December moment against Maryland in which Marcus Paige's attempt at an alley-oop dunk ended up giving Johnson an easy dunk.
videos.headline: Senior memories with Paige and Johnson

videos.description: 1H (8:03) UNC Theo Pinson made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Nate Britt.
videos.headline: Theo Pinson extends the Tar Heels lead with a 3.

videos.description: 1H (4:17) SYR Tyler Lydon missed Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Tyler Lydon airballs a 3-pointer with plenty of time on the shot clock.

videos.description: 1H (2:16) UNC Marcus Paige made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Marcus Paige hits a long 3-pointer, Trevor Cooney responds with an airball.

videos.description: North Carolina 3s help propel them to a first half lead.
videos.headline: North Carolina 3s help propel them to a first half lead.

videos.description: North Carolina's Marcus Paige delivers a sweet one-handed pass to Isaiah Hicks, who scores with a two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Paige dropping dimes on Syracuse

videos.description: With his mom in the crowd for North Carolina's senior night, Marcus Paige drives the lane, absorbs the contact and scores the layup.
videos.headline: Paige makes his mom proud with this and-1

videos.description: 2H (13:50) UNC Nate Britt missed Layup.
videos.headline: Nate Britt is found cutting down an open lane, but misses the easy layup.

videos.description: 2H (12:08) UNC Kennedy Meeks made Jumper. Assisted by Theo Pinson.
videos.headline: Roy Williams fired up after Meeks jumper.

videos.description: 2H (10:57) UNC Nate Britt made Layup.
videos.headline: Britt picks Syracuse's pocket and cashes in on a layup.

videos.description: Syracuse's Michael Gbinije soars into the lane and scores on a thunderous putback jam.
videos.headline: Michael Gbinije shows no mercy on the putback dunk

videos.description: 2H (7:55) UNC Brice Johnson made Layup. Assisted by Justin Jackson.
videos.headline: Tar Heels desperation passing leads to a Brice Johnson layup.

videos.description: 2H (6:16) UNC Justin Jackson made Layup.
videos.headline: Justin Jackson scores on Brice Johnsons outlet pass.

videos.description: 2H (3:16) SYR Tyler Roberson made Layup. Assisted by Michael Gbinije.
videos.headline: Gbinije to Roberson for the alley-oop layin that brings 'Cuse within 3.

videos.headline: Michael Gbinije hits the clutch 3-pointer.
